snippet.title: Sacred 3 - Official Gameplay Trailer [US]
snippet.description: Sacred 3 is coming Summer 2014 for PlayStation 3, Xbox 360 and PC. Pre-order now and visit www.sacred-world.com for more information. Victory is Ours. Glory is Mine.
